# ==============================================================================
# .gitignore — Peer-Review (Referee) Workflow
# ==============================================================================

# Manuscripts under review are usually confidential — don't commit input PDFs
# (including per-paper subfolders like papers/mypaper/). Delete these lines to
# track example papers in the repo.
papers/**/*.pdf
papers/**/*.PDF
papers/*.pdf
papers/*.PDF

# Referee pipeline scratch space (paper briefs, intermediates)
referee_reports/.work/

# Generated referee reports are the product (and often confidential) — don't
# commit them. README.md stays tracked as folder documentation.
referee_reports/referee_report_*.md

# Python
__pycache__/
*.pyc
*.pyo

# Claude Code local files (not shared across machines)
.claude/settings.local.json
.claude/state/
CLAUDE.local.md

# OS files
.DS_Store
Thumbs.db
*:Zone.Identifier

# IDE
.vscode/
.idea/
*.swp
*.swo
*~
